Hi Exhaust Systems Australia team,

We are preparing the Oak Flats Muffler Men online parts catalogue and need re=
al product images for the attached rows.

Please start with the 2 P1 rows because they are launch-blocking.

Current request split:

- P1 launch-blocking rows: 2
- P2 image request rows: 9
- P3 exception-review rows: 0
- Total rows in this supplier request: 11

Image requirements:

- Send one clean product image per row where possible.
- Use transparent PNG where available. Clean product-only JPG, PNG or WebP fi=
les are also accepted.
- Avoid watermarks, lifestyle-only photos, logos, favicons and placeholder im=
ages.
- Minimum 900 px on the longest edge is preferred if available.
- Name files by SKU or Source UID so the import can match them automatically.

Best filenames:

- SKU.png
- SourceUID.png

If a product genuinely has no image available, please mark that row as no ima=
ge available in the CSV and return it with the image export.

Requested files are included in the ZIP attachment:

- esa-p1.csv for P1 rows
- esa-all.csv for all missing-media rows
- esa-request.md for the full request notes

Thanks,
Oak Flats Muffler Men

